Interface ErrorTableInterface

Created 10-05-10

Changelog available at ErrorTableInterface.

All Known Implementing Classes:
ErrorTable
public interface ErrorTableInterface

Author:
Aaron D'Amico Error table is a flat text file. The name of this file is stored on the root directory of the code (As it is with all tables or files that need to be imported). This class has the methods to import this file into a data structure.
